31 holder's clinical activities. The supervising practitioner or a designated
32 respiratory care practitioner shall review and countersign the entries
33 that the permit holder makes in a patient's medical record not more
34 than seven (7) calendar days after the permit holder makes the entries.
35 (g) A supervising practitioner may not supervise at one (1) time
36 more than three (3) holders of student permits issued under this section.
